      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Totally Not Cool, Kulu!",
        "Client": "Yomogi the Chef",
        "Description": "A pair of \u003CCOL RED\u003EKulu-Ya-Ku\u003C/COL\u003E is after\r\nthe eggs I had dibs on for\r\nmy dango! No fair, AND\r\nrude! But if you can keep them\r\noccupied, I can grab the eggs\r\nbefore they eat \u0027em. You\u0027ll\r\nhelp me out, right? Right?",
